 From (film)|Where I'm From]] (D\u2019ou je viens)''\n*[[Nicolas Canniccioni]], ''[[Guidelines (film)|Guidelines]] (La marche \u00e0 suivre)''\n*[[Marie Davignon]], [[Jessica Lee Gagn\u00e9]], [[Genevi\u00e8ve Perron]], ''[[All That We Make]] (Fermi\u00e8res)''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''[[Reginald Harkema]] and [[Alex Shuper]], ''[[Super Duper Alice Cooper]]'''''\n*[[Mathieu Bouchard-Malo]], ''[[Guidelines (film)|Guidelines]] (La marche \u00e0 suivre)''\n*[[Tony Girardin]], ''[[Marinoni: The Fire in the Frame]]''\n*[[Robert Kennedy (editor)|Robert Kennedy]], ''[[Altman (film)|Altman]]''\n*[[Myriam Magassouba]], ''[[All That We Make]] (Fermi\u00e8res)''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | [[Claude Jutra Award]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | [[Golden Screen Award (Canada)|Golden Screen Award]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''[[Jeffrey St. Jules]], ''[[Bang Bang Baby]]'''''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''''[[Pompeii (film)|Pompeii]]'''''\n|}\n\n==Television==\n\n===Programs===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | [[Academy of Canadian Cinema and Television Award for Best Dramatic Series|Drama series]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | [[Academy of Canadian Cinema and Television Award for Best Comedy Series|Comedy series]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''''[[Orphan Black]]'''''\n*''[[19-2 (2014 TV series)|19-2]]''\n*''[[Continuum (TV series)|Continuum]]''\n*''[[Motive (TV series)|Motive]]''\n*''[[Remedy (TV series)|Remedy]]''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''''[[Call Me Fitz]]'''''\n*''[[Mr. D]]''\n*''[[Seed (TV series)|Seed]]''\n*''[[Spun Out]]''\n*''[[Tiny Plastic Men]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | Animated program or series\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | Documentary program\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''''[[Rocket Monkeys]]'''''\n*''[[Fangbone!]]''\n*''[[Grojband]