ir]], ''[[Sex & Violence (TV series)|Sex & Violence]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | Performance in an animated program or series\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | Performance in a variety or sketch comedy program or series\n|-\n| valign=\"top |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''[[Scott McCord]], ''[[Justin Time (TV series)|Justin Time]]'''''\n*[[Dan Chameroy]], ''[[Oh No! It's an Alien Invasion]]''\n*[[Sean Cullen]], ''[[Oh No! It's an Alien Invasion]]''\n*[[Mark Edwards (actor)|Mark Edwards]], ''[[Rocket Monkeys]]''\n*[[Julie Lemieux]], ''[[Dinopaws]]''\n| valign=\"top |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''[[Rick Mercer]], ''[[Rick Mercer Report]]'''''\n*[[Mark Critch]], [[Cathy Jones]], [[Susan Kent (actress)|Susan Kent]] and [[Shaun Majumder]], ''[[This Hour Has 22 Minutes]]''\n*[[Jon Dore]], ''[[Funny as Hell]]''\n*[[Kira Isabella]], ''[[Studio 14 Sessions]]''\n*[[Johnny Reid]], ''[[Johnny Reid|Johnny Reid: A Christmas Gift to You]]''\n|}\n\n===News and information===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | News special\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%\" | News reportage, local\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*{{blue ribbon}} '''[[CBC News]] (''[[The National (CBC)|The National]]'', [[CBC News Network]] and [[CBAT-DT|CBC New Brunswick]]), ''[[2014 Moncton shootings|Moncton Shooting: The Capture of Justin Bourque]]'' - Derek Desouza, Mark Harrison, Darrow MacIntyre, Mark Ross, Kate Scroggins\n*[[CIII-DT|Global Ontario]], ''[[2014 Ontario general election|Decision Ontario]]'' - Wayne Hardie, Michael Hennigar, Sharon Murphy, Amy Saracino, Dave Trafford, Mark Trueman'''\n*[[CBMT-DT|CBC Montreal]], ''[[2014 Quebec general election|CBC News: Quebec Votes 2014]]'' - Debra Arbec, [[Andrew Chang]], Catherine Cullen, Peter Johnson, Nancy Wood\n*[[CP24]], ''[[2014 Ontario general election|Your Vote 2014: The Race for Ontario]]'' - Brian Carr, Troy Gallant, Murray King, Joanne MacDonald, Linda Oland, Liana Vangelisti, Stacy Voudouris\n| val